text: Electric Callboy (formerly known as Eskimo Callboy) is a German electronicore band. They were founded in Castrop-Rauxel in 2010. The current members are Kevin Ratajczak, Daniel "Danskimo" Hani√ü, Pascal Schillo, Daniel Klossek, David Friedrich and Nico Sallach.
